r, \'both\')\n    94\t    AND 6371 * ACOS(\n    95\t      COS(RADIANS(当前用户纬
度)) * COS(RADIANS(up.latitude)) * COS(RADIANS(up.longitude) - RADIANS(当前用户
经度))\n    96\t      + SIN(RADIANS(当前用户纬度)) * SIN(RADIANS(up.latitude))\n
   97\t    ) <= max_distance\n    98\t    AND u.id NOT IN (已滑动、已匹配、已拉
黑的用户子查询)\n    99\t  ```\n   100\t\n   101\t1.3 **缓存与锁**\n   102\t- Re
